==English==

===Etymology===
Representing ''localization'' as "L" followed by 10 more letters, followed by "n".

===Noun===
'''L10n'''

# {{softeng}} [[Localization]].

===Alternative forms===
*'''l10N'''

====Usage notes====
*The preferred spelling is '''L10n''', as the lower-case ''l'' ("el") is indistinguishable from an upper-case ''I'' ("eye") in many [[sans serif]] [[font]]s.

